    <item>
      <title>Daily Security News from @trustpath - May 3, 2017</title>
      <link>//crypt0.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2017-05-03/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 May 2017 18:05:01 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>//crypt0.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2017-05-03/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Daily Security news from &lt;a href=&#34;http://twitter.com/trustpath&#34;&gt;@trustpath&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Data breach investigations report shows 50% rise in ransomware attacks&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A recent report from Juniper Research found that, despite significant investment in cybersecurity, data breaches will have cost the global business &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.bizreport.com/2017/05/data-breach-investigations-report-shows-50-rise-in-ransomwar.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.bizreport.com/2017/05/data-breach-investigations-report-shows-50-rise-in-ransomwar.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Healthcare data breaches skyrocket, but is there good news coming?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In 2016, 328 individual healthcare breaches occurred, surpassing the previous record of 268 in 2015, according to Bitglass&amp;rsquo; recent Healthcare Breach &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.networkworld.com/article/3192885/healthcare/healthcare-data-breaches-skyrocket-but-is-there-good-news-coming.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.networkworld.com/article/3192885/healthcare/healthcare-data-breaches-skyrocket-but-is-there-good-news-coming.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Over USD 5 billion insurable loss each year to US businesses through data&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Romanian Insurance 1asig.ro Data breaches can cost companies hundreds of millions of dollars, the loss potentially reaching USD 5 billion a year across the USA only from data &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://insurance.1asig.ro/Over-USD-5-billion-insurable-loss-each-year-to-U-S-businesses-through-data-exfiltration-article-2,3,100-9376.htm&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://insurance.1asig.ro/Over-USD-5-billion-insurable-loss-each-year-to-U-S-businesses-through-data-exfiltration-article-2,3,100-9376.htm&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;BeyondTrust Survey Links Breaches to Aging Federal Infrastructure&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The total cost due for data breaches is $637 million every year. The most frequently reported costs include loss of productivity, loss of reputation and &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.marketwired.com/press-release/beyondtrust-survey-links-breaches-to-aging-federal-infrastructure-2213758.htm&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.marketwired.com/press-release/beyondtrust-survey-links-breaches-to-aging-federal-infrastructure-2213758.htm&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Healthcare breaches down following 2016 peak&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Healthcare data breaches hit an all-time high in 2016 resulting in the records of almost 16.6 million Americans being exposed as a result of hacks, lost &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://betanews.com/2017/05/03/healthcare-breaches-down/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://betanews.com/2017/05/03/healthcare-breaches-down/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Hackers cast a wider net in launching cyber attacks&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;database that tracks data breaches, found nearly 1.4 billion records were &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://thirdcertainty.com/infographics/hackers-cast-a-wider-net-in-launching-cyber-attacks/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://thirdcertainty.com/infographics/hackers-cast-a-wider-net-in-launching-cyber-attacks/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Palo Alto Networks Expands its Traps Advanced Endpoint Protection&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Palo Alto Networks announced enhancements to its Traps advanced endpoint protection offering that strengthen its malware and exploit prevention &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.dqindia.com/palo-alto-networks-expands-its-traps-advanced-endpoint-protection/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.dqindia.com/palo-alto-networks-expands-its-traps-advanced-endpoint-protection/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Thales 2017 Report: 96% Federal Workers Fear Data Breaches&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The report indicated that ninety six percent of federal workers consider themselves very or extremely vulnerable to data breaches. This number is &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://blog.executivebiz.com/2017/05/thales-releases-2017-data-threat-report/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://blog.executivebiz.com/2017/05/thales-releases-2017-data-threat-report/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Lastline Showcasing Advanced Malware Protection at May Events Across the&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Yahoo Finance &amp;hellip; of advanced malware protection and are seeking us out at these events to learn how Lastline can eliminate data breaches with a very low TCO.&amp;ldquo;.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://finance.yahoo.com/news/lastline-showcasing-advanced-malware-protection-150000201.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://finance.yahoo.com/news/lastline-showcasing-advanced-malware-protection-150000201.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Tech-Savvy Innovative Hotels Are More Vulnerable to Data Breaches&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The race to become the most innovated and tech-savvy hotel is on. Hotels have increasingly begun working with technology companies to offer more &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://hospitalitytechnology.edgl.com/news/Tech-Savvy-Innovative-Hotels-Are-More-Vulnerable-to-Data-Breaches109553&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://hospitalitytechnology.edgl.com/news/Tech-Savvy-Innovative-Hotels-Are-More-Vulnerable-to-Data-Breaches109553&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Report Finds 16.6M Affected by 2016 Healthcare Data Breaches&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Report Finds 16.6M Affected by 2016 Healthcare Data Breaches. A recent Bitglass report found that hacking and IT incidents continue to pose the &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://healthitsecurity.com/news/report-finds-16.6m-affected-by-2016-healthcare-data-breaches&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://healthitsecurity.com/news/report-finds-16.6m-affected-by-2016-healthcare-data-breaches&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Physical Security Information Management(PSIM) Market Analytical Overview,&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Green Mountain Outlook Physical Security Information Management(PSIM) Market Report provides an analytical assessment of the prime challenges faced by this Market &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.gmoutlook.com/physical-security-information-managementpsim-market-analytical-overview-growth-factors-demand-and-trends-forecast-report-till-2022-24613.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.gmoutlook.com/physical-security-information-managementpsim-market-analytical-overview-growth-factors-demand-and-trends-forecast-report-till-2022-24613.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Healthcare providers&amp;rsquo; cybersecurity tools may need an upgrade&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;And a study by the Brookings Institution predicts that one in four data breaches this year will hit the healthcare industry. Accenture&amp;rsquo;s website stated &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.nurse.com/blog/2017/05/03/providers-need-better-data-security-from-hackers/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.nurse.com/blog/2017/05/03/providers-need-better-data-security-from-hackers/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Report: Healthcare Data Breaches Hit Record High In 2016&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;increase from 268 the previous year and setting a new all-time high for &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.tripwire.com/state-of-security/latest-security-news/report-healthcare-data-breaches-hit-record-high-2016/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.tripwire.com/state-of-security/latest-security-news/report-healthcare-data-breaches-hit-record-high-2016/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Data breach case against Schnuck Markets dismissed&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;hellip; chain Schnuck Markets Inc. in connection with a data breach it suffered in 2012 and 2013, citing the prevalence of data breaches during that period.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.businessinsurance.com/article/20170503/NEWS06/912313250/Schnuck-Markets-data-breach-lawsuit&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.businessinsurance.com/article/20170503/NEWS06/912313250/Schnuck-Markets-data-breach-lawsuit&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;The Top 5 Myths Of Next-Gen Endpoint Protection&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Top 5 Myths Of Next-Gen Endpoint Protection. Trend Micro. &amp;lsquo;Next-generation&amp;rsquo; endpoint protection or next-gen AV has been getting a lot of press &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.techrepublic.com/resource-library/whitepapers/the-top-5-myths-of-next-gen-endpoint-protection/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.techrepublic.com/resource-library/whitepapers/the-top-5-myths-of-next-gen-endpoint-protection/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Survey: 42 Percent of Fed IT Managers Hacked in Past 6 Mos.&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Across the federal IT systems, data breaches are estimated to cost $637 million each year, The Hill reported. The survey also found 61 percent of &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.newsmax.com/US/federal-information-technology-hacked/2017/05/03/id/787973/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.newsmax.com/US/federal-information-technology-hacked/2017/05/03/id/787973/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Global trends in public sector data breaches revealed in new report&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The tenth edition of Verizon&amp;rsquo;s very readable yearly Data Breach Investigation Report is out, with analysis of 239 confirmed data breaches that affected &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.themandarin.com.au/78558-global-trends-in-cyber-security-show-governments-are-slow-to-detect-breaches/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.themandarin.com.au/78558-global-trends-in-cyber-security-show-governments-are-slow-to-detect-breaches/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
